title: Beautiful 2BR in Nordeast Minneapolis
posting_body: ['Now showing for Mid August or September 1st occupancy: Spacious, 2 bedroom apartment in quiet, friendly residential Nordeast Minneapolis neighborhood.', 'Beautiful, updated 1st-floor unit in historic 1906 house - just the place to be: walk and bike to nearby Northeast brewpubs, coffeehouses and restaurants; near bus lines, bike trails and close to everything.', 'Traditional 1900s claw-foot tub and stained glass windows are complimented by the newly remodeled 21st century updates: Newer carpeted living room, dining room and bedrooms with enlarged closets; spacious, remodeled kitchen has newer cabinetry, linoleum, counters and appliances with large pantry and lots of cupboards; bright, remodeled bathroom with bathtub/shower.', 'Large deck, beautiful garden and well-maintained yard and property with newer siding, roof and Solar panels.', 'Solar panels also have battery backup to provide some light/heat if ever needed.', 'One of the nicest rentals in NE.', '$1595/month rent.', 'Wireless internet is included.', 'Renter pays own gas and electric (aprox $180 MO with Budget).', '1-month security deposit and 1st-month rent required at signing.', 'Rental criteria: Income must be 2.5 times rent.', 'No outstanding judgements.', 'No smoking on the property.', 'Pets', 'Cats allowed', 'Lease description', 'Wireless internet is included.', 'Renter pays gas and electric.', 'Owner pays water, sewer and trash hauling.', 'Lease renewal term to be negotiated (1-2year term)']
